{"tid":1348523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完林鄭個記招，正式宣佈唔止警犬係condom","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:53:19.000Z","uid":72209,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8dfd98fef76a110a5a5db7ddd84070fc9a2f2cf","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:22:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有果班盲撐政府嘅藍絲，左膠，中立派。</span></span></strong><br />\n七一衝立法會果時，爛塊玻璃就一齊同政府譴責暴力，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為虎作倀</span></span></strong>。<br />\n而家到真係有暴力事件發生，班鄉黑唔理你咩人都照打，先發現政府由頭到尾冇care過你地嘅安全？？<br />\n<br />\n發唔發現林鄭個記招，只係好籠統咁譴責元朗暴力事件，唔會針對白衣人士，弦外之音就係，尋日有份出現嘅所有人，都係暴徒，各打五十大板，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">理撚得你係咪只係路過比人打？</span></span></strong><br />\n市民安全？都重要嘅，不過點都唔夠「一國兩制」咁<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「至為重要」囉。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以話你班藍絲，左膠，中立派幾犯賤，幫完政府譴責暴力，到真正嘅暴力發生喺你地身上，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地只係一個用完即棄嘅condom，一國兩制重要過你，國徽重要過你，連立法會塊玻璃都矜貴過你地條賤命。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n建議以後喺facebook搞文宣，就直接笑呢班廢老係condom啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"4f7cfa02f3f4bd4b207053e9f6cb723ff79f7dab","tid":1348523,"uid":146621,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"如果佢認真<br />\n黑社會都係condom<br />\n啱啱三巨頭先話割蓆"},{"pid":"2a874fc59a0fb6b4a620647812703b75f003d7b0","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"仲有，<br />\n<br />\n尋日喺MTR，有個師奶好撚驚咁問我點解MTR會唔開車，點解報咗警都未解決到，又話如果唔係自己親眼見到都唔知社會咁痴線。<br />\n<br />\n到屯門落車臨走果時講咗句：「以後唔再支持警察喇，都做唔到野。」<br />\n<br />\n哈。"},{"pid":"3e411bc000bad0c06dec51b93c3979042ef75170","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4f7cfa02f3f4bd4b207053e9f6cb723ff79f7dab","tid":1348523,"uid":146621,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"如果佢認真<br />\n黑社會都係condom<br />\n啱啱三巨頭先話割蓆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"所有人都係政府嘅condom，而香港政府係中共嘅condom。"},{"pid":"ef8819b7dbf6c10d0004324101a8c98c6f9f17a2","tid":1348523,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"何君妖就快被黑社會清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b3b05022f7b41def60c2f75fdfa872a25318d3","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"大家趁而家落力啲感化屋企啲藍絲啦，今次都唔轉軚，以後都唔會轉到㗎喇。"},{"pid":"ea1fc55338cde0f944ea6352d4b582158eda0195","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef8819b7dbf6c10d0004324101a8c98c6f9f17a2","tid":1348523,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"何君妖就快被黑社會清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"何君堯真係好撚嘔心，到時要全香港一齊清算佢。"},{"pid":"aaf86993f519b47d44df4149d097d12fd4b68df7","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"e4361c41d0a5b977c8155d08e7fb7d28db197a64","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"98af3b532ac85c14f7282098b28eca7b484d0e19","tid":1348523,"uid":72209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"pushhh"},{"pid":"5cd1a4